text: "Made in England" is a 1995 song by Elton John and is the title track from their 24th studio album Made in England. It went to number 52 in the United States, number 18 in the United Kingdom, number 19 in Scotland, number 17 in Iceland, number 20 in Norway and number 5 in Canada. ==References== Category:1995 songs Category:Elton John songs Category:Pop rock songs
